 /><br />\n<br />\n你不如比佢食一排好番啲先再諗轉野<br />\n<br />\n真係要supplement可以考慮吓K-Plus"},{"pid":"2f32c8219f2bae60cb0567f93ec32dbcf044d829","tid":2024020,"uid":144828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:04:57.000Z","msg":"我家主子都係異國短毛貓,都有秘尿結石結石問題<br />\n以前都聽聞囂屎同Royal唔太好,多味精,所以我會等佢好返再轉啲貴啲對貓貓好啲天然啲既糧<br />\n但係我無論點轉貓糧,轉幾貴都好都會翻發,我發現咁其實害左佢<br />\n所以為左佢我都認命,依家一直食緊囂屎處方糧,Touch wood 冇發幾年了,<br />\n不過就食極唔肥.<br />\n附上主子圖一張<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yEkxza0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyEkxza0.jpg&h=83ba721e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68099c511b43a42e257b49144262412bb1a53a0b","tid":2024020,"uid":132639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33b87d2338fc88f0c4fe85ec1a84bb3e11e014a1","tid":2024020,"uid":51571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T08:53:04.000Z","msg":"屋企老貓之前都腎功能差<br />\n<br />\n而家長期食hills 都無事 控制得幾好<br />\n<br />\n其實隻煙無你諗咁差，獸醫糧有佢既設計原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你不如比佢食一排好番啲先再諗轉野<br />\n<br />\n真係要supplement可以考慮吓K-Plus"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:15:46.000Z","msg":"可能真係唯有認命食hills,為左佢健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569046ae5bc23fb4fc5f2075f1510da866650de5","tid":2024020,"uid":249293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:28:38.000Z","msg":"最慘係屋企有2隻貓 食既野都唔一樣 佢地成日對住大家兜糧虎視眈眈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2585e01a53883e71a37250f7a86928d8d2b0ce6","tid":2024020,"uid":19004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:09:43.000Z","msg":"Hills cd 罐有無食"},{"pid":"02fd01b173eb493c1cb72adc019ec027b565bead","tid":2024020,"uid":132639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2585e01a53883e71a37250f7a86928d8d2b0ce6","tid":2024020,"uid":19004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:09:43.000Z","msg":"Hills cd 罐有無食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:27:36.000Z","msg":"有呀<br />\n罐同乾糧都有食"},{"pid":"ed4f25e697cad37c0b6341b6bc05b450545b9a42","tid":2024020,"uid":132639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"569046ae5bc23fb4fc5f2075f1510da866650de5","tid":2024020,"uid":249293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:28:38.000Z","msg":"最慘係屋企有2隻貓 食既野都唔一樣 佢地成日對住大家兜糧虎視眈眈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:28:02.000Z","msg":"隔離飯香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f185877d642e88c0cd28df55552c6d9f3427c575","tid":2024020,"uid":342884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:31:32.000Z","msg":"想問有咩病徵嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"1095914fe2b1452b23537b880c51332d13378d2e","tid":2024020,"uid":78369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T16:12:24.000Z","msg":"首先貓貓係天生唔鐘意飲水 因為佢哋本身係肉食動物 會係新鮮肉類吸收水份 呢個係天性 然後男仔會比女仔易有泌尿問題 因為佢地尿道比較曲折同complex. <br />\n<br />\n要預防/改善泌尿問題 你可以做足以下幾點:<br />\n<br />\n1. 用water fountain. 流動嘅水容易吸引貓貓去飲 keep住過濾會比較乾淨新鮮(推薦petkit, 因為濾芯係活性碳唔係普通一舊棉 咩柒都格唔到)<br />\n<br />\n2. 增加濕糧ratio. 50:50 or higher. 濕糧最好揀complete meal嘅罐頭 唔係普通零食罐頭 而且日本嗰啲多味精<br />\n<br />\n3. 生肉糧 (optional, 睇你隻貓接唔接受到  最天然嘅食物對佢哋黎講)<br />\n<br />\n4. 乾糧轉泌尿專用糧 (我屋企嗰隻食緊RC urinary S/O LP34, so far 覺得最好) 提一提揀糧都要睇埋ingredients. 唔好揀啲頭5樣都係啲咩chicken meal, salmon meal, pea.......呢啲係肉粉唔係真肉 簡單啲講就係加工食品 至於grain free呢啲係基本<br />\n<br />\n5. 多清潔貓砂盆！！(起碼一日一兩次 得閒要洗埋)呢個好重要 佢哋聞到有味會忍尿 忍得多就會易有尿石 唔好諗住用啲有香味嘅貓砂或deodorizer就算 因為貓嘅嗅覺好敏感 其實香味對佢哋係唔好嘅 (用木粒 遇水變粉貓砂最好 病貓都用得 低粉塵 環保 想知再講)柯屎都大有學問啦總之<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 用貓hormone嘅diffuser (feline cat) 原理係比佢哋聞到有貓味 環境安全 安心小壓力<br />\n<br />\n7. 唔好亂搬嘢亂帶人翻屋企 因為味道唔用咗貓貓心情受大影響會令佢哋壓力大而唔柯尿<br />\n<br />\n利申: 隻衰仔入過兩次醫院 非打手<br />\n<br />\n最後。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y43Lb6P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY43Lb6P.png&h=0444fead&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1c9a30f2ff225dddaa44ba6f1b7da3451a1e990","tid":2024020,"uid":132639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1095914fe2b1452b23537b880c51332d13378d2e","tid":2024020,"uid":78369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T16:12:24.000Z","msg":"首先貓貓係天生唔鐘意飲水 因為佢哋本身係肉食動物 會係新鮮肉類吸收水份 呢個係天性 然後男仔會比女仔易有泌尿問題 因為佢地尿道比較曲折同complex. <br />\n<br />\n要預防/改善泌尿問題 你可以做足以下幾點:<br />\n<br />\n1. 用water fountain. 流動嘅水容易吸引貓貓去飲 keep住過濾會比較乾淨新鮮(推薦petkit, 因為濾芯係活性碳唔係普通一舊棉 咩柒都格唔到)<br />\n<br />\n2. 增加濕糧ratio. 50:50 or higher. 濕糧最好揀complete meal嘅罐頭 唔係普通零食罐頭 而且日本嗰啲多味精<br />\n<br />\n3. 生肉糧 (optional, 睇你隻貓接唔接受到  最天然嘅食物對佢哋黎講)<br />\n<br />\n4. 乾糧轉泌尿專用糧 (我屋企嗰隻食緊RC urinary S/O LP34, so far 覺得最好) 提一提揀糧都要睇埋ingredients. 唔好揀啲頭5樣都係啲咩chicken meal, salmon meal, pea.......呢啲係肉粉唔係真肉 簡單啲講就係加工食品 至於grain free呢啲係基本<br />\n<br />\n5. 多清潔貓砂盆！！(起碼一日一兩次 得閒要洗埋)呢個好重要 佢哋聞到有味會忍尿 忍得多就會易有尿石 唔好諗住用啲有香味嘅貓砂或deodorizer就算 因為貓嘅嗅覺好敏感 其實香味對佢哋係唔好嘅 (用木粒 遇水變粉貓砂最好 病貓都用得 低粉塵 環保 想知再講)柯屎都大有學問啦總之<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 用貓hormone嘅diffuser (feline cat) 原理係比佢哋聞到有貓味 環境安全 安心小壓力<br />\n<br />\n7. 唔好亂搬嘢亂帶人翻屋企 因為味道唔用咗貓貓心情受大影響會令佢哋壓力大而唔柯尿<br />\n<br />\n利申: 隻衰仔入過兩次醫院 非打手<br />\n<br />\n最後。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y43Lb6P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY43Lb6P.png&h=0444fead&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:52:06.000Z","msg":"巴打好詳細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主子好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1，2，5同我之前都有做一路做緊<br />\n同埋其實佢唔多怕生人<br />\n食好玩好訓好<br />\n但就係時不時就突然復發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次諗住真係疊埋心水俾俾佢長期食處方糧算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打有冇試過hills?<br />\nRc定hills好?<br />\n為表答謝<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a304777a9d49e33baa5acb7a1a1083d40967fb0","tid":2024020,"uid":143405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c53543f90fba4f59226bf9a90a380c69c028e601","tid":2024020,"uid":132639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e01befc540713866b86217bf930e4b2d7b3da47f","tid":2024020,"uid":7929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed4a215316ed65d3071a50b289e792113b83d6cc","tid":2024020,"uid":132639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:10:44.000Z","msg":"我隻主子1歲幾，之前試過秘尿結石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好番過一排又復發，前前後後已經持續左半年<br />\n平時已經轉哂一日一餐濕糧，兩餐濕+乾糧<br />\n睇醫生就俾囂屎處方糧，仲話可以長期食<br />\n但我真係唔想隻主子長期食囂屎垃圾肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該點做改善呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:14:00.000Z","msg":"係好難<br />\n我個隻每1-2年就入院做手術<br />\n好咀diu. 要人手餵糧<br />\n已經食得好清"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:24:33.000Z","msg":"其實關唔關隻主子心情事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢排太忙少陪佢玩<br />\n定係男仔容易奶野多d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T21:12:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9330485711aaadc21b4f60811cf27c4badeffca3","tid":2024020,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T21:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e19ba998e32efc93f9e47a68a26e00eeb52a2c4","tid":2024020,"uid":143405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3234f6556a342bc37d44db292b7de80d83d6d15","tid":2024020,"uid":54092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"353d261b85cb1