 因為貓嘅嗅覺好敏感 其實香味對佢哋係唔好嘅 (用木粒 遇水變粉貓砂最好 病貓都用得 低粉塵 環保 想知再講)柯屎都大有學問啦總之<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 用貓hormone嘅diffuser (feline cat) 原理係比佢哋聞到有貓味 環境安全 安心小壓力<br />\n<br />\n7. 唔好亂搬嘢亂帶人翻屋企 因為味道唔用咗貓貓心情受大影響會令佢哋壓力大而唔柯尿<br />\n<br />\n利申: 隻衰仔入過兩次醫院 非打手<br />\n<br />\n最後。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y43Lb6P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY43Lb6P.png&h=0444fead&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:52:06.000Z","msg":"巴打好詳細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主子好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1，2，5同我之前都有做一路做緊<br />\n同埋其實佢唔多怕生人<br />\n食好玩好訓好<br />\n但就係時不時就突然復發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次諗住真係疊埋心水俾俾佢長期食處方糧算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打有冇試過hills?<br />\nRc定hills好?<br />\n為表答謝<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:20:26.000Z","msg":"姑娘當時有比hills and RC samples我 <br />\n我主子鐘意食RC多啲 成份好小小 以前做pet food research所以我都揀宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以家係食一包RC, 就食翻兩三個月普通糧 好似人要飲下涼茶飲下湯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />長期食有藥用價值嘅嘢食 我怕會食純咗。。。。。<br />\n普通糧依家係食vigor &amp; sage, 無翻發 成份靚 又有天然補品咩紀子人參啊荷葉啊<br />\n<br />\n另一隻肥貓會因為唔po佢嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tdkmyA6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtdkmyA6.jpg&h=2aa0c89b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5NzZkf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5NzZkf7.jpg&h=e0bab2e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2eSDAPx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2eSDAPx.png&h=20ac10ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TW3OX2W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTW3OX2W.png&h=b19d1483&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r03WnuH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr03WnuH.png&h=990b6153&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02b50dcf8f3f09ab23c5515f0d8114f2dae002ef","tid":2024020,"uid":131843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27544e9a521fc20f03e79e026865af9037e41dea","tid":2024020,"uid":132639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38376b1ac46cdb7805c6057b067f15f7a52e93e9","tid":2024020,"uid":54092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bf406449b15e0aabd236874af0b4c3590609d05","tid":2024020,"uid":132639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:26:13.000Z","msg":"係咪濕糧都係代替唔到清水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢都係唔中意飲水，所以我先俾罐罐加水加乾糧餵佢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:34:30.000Z","msg":"我隻貓有相同問題，已人手餵濕糧兩年（係每日無間斷）...<br />\n<br />\n記住濕糧加水去餵， 我隻貓每日都屙好多尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:36:28.000Z","msg":"我之前試過一排，全濕糧加水<br />\n但變相3，4日先屙一次屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:23:55.000Z","msg":"其實濕糧幾乎會吸收晒，幾日先開一次大都正常"},{"pid":"75e85fd79fb5dbd3fd5f148c3b8fdff450c25f99","tid":2024020,"uid":205416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:43:17.000Z","msg":"係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fd077a87b99727925ba9d0557213f9ae3ed060","tid":2024020,"uid":205416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74a82a39833f28e8feeddb4931eddbd196598ce9","tid":2024020,"uid":132639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c59cf00a0e2f8d2dcefd95b81b72823fc0cd5a7","tid":2024020,"uid":205416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T01:36:51.000Z","msg":"得個隻細個時尿道有事，最後長期食RC 處方糧，食到而家差唔多十年了<br />\n<br />\n連無事啲貓仔都食埋（佢地貪隔離糧香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），後來問過醫生話可以食，因為隻糧主要令貓仔口渴飲多啲水"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T08:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6N1wPxJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6N1wPxJ.png&h=2efb2a64&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n絲打係食呢隻?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:44:49.000Z","msg":"係呀"},{"pid":"3e04ec4604e43a4278129bb6a6b54b683a2dc3c4","tid":2024020,"uid":132639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43f597a474035f4ef1c204484f8f9544ab9ce69d","tid":2024020,"uid":78369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1c9a30f2ff225dddaa44ba6f1b7da3451a1e990","tid":2024020,"uid":132639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1095914fe2b1452b23537b880c51332d13378d2e","tid":2024020,"uid":78369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T16:12:24.000Z","msg":"首先貓貓係天生唔鐘意飲水 因為佢哋本身係肉食動物 會係新鮮肉類吸收水份 呢個係天性 然後男仔會比女仔易有泌尿問題 因為佢地尿道比較曲折同complex. <br />\n<br />\n要預防/改善泌尿問題 你可以做足以下幾點:<br />\n<br />\n1. 用water fountain. 流動嘅水容易吸引貓貓去飲 keep住過濾會比較乾淨新鮮(推薦petkit, 因為濾芯係活性碳唔係普通一舊棉 咩柒都格唔到)<br />\n<br />\n2. 增加濕糧ratio. 50:50 or higher. 濕糧最好揀complete meal嘅罐頭 唔係普通零食罐頭 而且日本嗰啲多味精<br />\n<br />\n3. 生肉糧 (optional, 睇你隻貓接唔接受到  最天然嘅食物對佢哋黎講)<br />\n<br />\n4. 乾糧轉泌尿專用糧 (我屋企嗰隻食緊RC urinary S/O LP34, so far 覺得最好) 提一提揀糧都要睇埋ingredients. 唔好揀啲頭5樣都係啲咩chicken meal, salmon meal, pea.......呢啲係肉粉唔係真肉 簡單啲講就係加工食品 至於grain free呢啲係基本<br />\n<br />\n5. 多清潔貓砂盆！！(起碼一日一兩次 得閒要洗埋)呢個好重要 佢哋聞到有味會忍尿 忍得多就會易有尿石 唔好諗住用啲有香味嘅貓砂或deodorizer就算 因為貓嘅嗅覺好敏感 其實香味對佢哋係唔好嘅 (用木粒 遇水變粉貓砂最好 病貓都用得 低粉塵 環保 想知再講)柯屎都大有學問啦總之<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 用貓hormone嘅diffuser (feline cat) 原理係比佢哋聞到有貓味 環境安全 安心小壓力<br />\n<br />\n7. 唔好亂搬嘢亂帶人翻屋企 因為味道唔用咗貓貓心情受大影響會令佢哋壓力大而唔柯尿<br />\n<br />\n利申: 隻衰仔入過兩次醫院 非打手<br />\n<br />\n最後。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y43Lb6P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY43Lb6P.png&h=0444fead&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T18:52:06.000Z","msg":"巴打好詳細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主子好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1，2，5同我之前都有做一路做緊<br />\n同埋其實佢唔多怕生人<br />\n食好玩好訓好<br />\n但就係時不時就突然復發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次諗住真係疊埋心水俾俾佢長期食處方糧算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打有冇試過hills?<br />\nRc定hills好?<br />\n為表答謝<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:20:26.000Z","msg":"姑娘當時有比hills and RC samples我 <br />\n我主子鐘意食RC多啲 成份好小小 以前做pet food research所以我都揀宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以家係食一包RC, 就食翻兩三個月普通糧 好似人要飲下涼茶飲下湯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />長期食有藥用價值嘅嘢食 我怕會食純咗。。。。。<br />\n普通糧依家係食vigor &amp; sage, 無翻發 成份靚 又有天然補品咩紀子人參啊荷葉啊<br />\n<br />\n另一隻肥貓會因為唔po佢嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tdkmyA6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtdkmyA6.jpg&h=2aa0c89b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5NzZkf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5NzZkf7.jpg&h=e0bab2e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2eSDAPx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2eSDAPx.png&h=20ac10ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TW3OX2W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTW3OX2W.png&h=b19d1483&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r03WnuH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr03WnuH.png&h=990b6153&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:33:42.000Z","msg":"請教咁樣轉糧法你隻貓貓一開頭有冇唔慣<br />\n即係一個月rc,兩三個月普通糧"}]}